{"ProductId":"291","Title":"Reserve<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Wood Extira<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup>","ShortDescription":"Enjoy the craftsmanship of an Extira wood door that offers lasting style and performance","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/reservewood-extira-slshowcase.webp?sfvrsn=2a687638_1","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/extira","Overview":"<h3>Elevate Your Home with Lasting Style</h3><h4>Strong 4-Layer Build</h4><p>Features Extira overlay and base, a polystyrene-insulated Hemlock frame, and a 2\" Luan backer for strength and durability.</p><h4>Eco-Friendly Composite</h4><p>Made from patented, sustainable materials, Extira resists moisture, rot, and termites while delivering the look and feel of genuine wood&mdash;without the flaws.</p><h4>Limitless Design Options</h4><p>Choose smooth or grooved panels, add deep V-grooves, arches, or curves&mdash;details that aren&rsquo;t possible with most garage doors. The surface is knot-free for a flawless, furniture-quality paint finish.</p><h4>Custom Colors &amp; Finishes</h4><p>Select from 1,500+ <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg;</a> paint shades to match your style. The paint-grade wood composite ensures a crisp, even finish every time.</p><h4>Energy Efficiency Built In</h4><p><a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/garage-door-materials/insulation\">Polystyrene insulation</a> (R-value 5.9) keeps your garage more comfortable year-round and helps with energy savings.</p><h4>Built for Any Climate</h4><p>Ask about <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement</a> for extra protection in high-wind areas.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Extira is a patented and proprietary wood composite manufactured from certified ecofriendly materials.</p><ul><li>Contains wood that has no commercial timber value and is the byproduct of other operations.</li><li>Certified by Scientific Certification Systems under certificate number SCS-MC-01802 to contain no added urea-formaldehyde.</li><li>Acknowledged by the California Air Resources Board&rsquo;s (CARB) Airborne Toxic Control Measure (ATCM) 93120 to use exempt status ultra-low emitting\r\n        formaldehyde (ULEF) resins.</li><li>Contributes to industry green building programs such as LEED and the National Green Building Standard.</li></ul><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>Solid Construction, Worry-Free Living</h3><p>Every Reserve&reg; Wood Extira&reg; garage door is crafted with durability and minimal maintenance in mind. At its core is a solid Hemlock wood frame, chosen for its natural strength and stability. This frame is wrapped and banded to seal out moisture, so your door stands up to the elements year after year.</p><p>A thick Extira&reg; overlay forms the exterior, delivering the look of high-end wood with exceptional resistance to rot, termites, and swelling. Inside, polystyrene insulation keeps your garage more comfortable, while a smooth 1/4\" Luan backer creates a clean, paintable finish for the interior face.</p><p>Special touches&mdash;like three-section construction for larger window openings and a unique one-piece drip cap&mdash;help keep water out and preserve the beauty of the door. True divided windows, premium hardware, and smooth-gliding rollers ensure quiet, reliable operation. A replaceable vinyl weather seal along the bottom keeps out drafts and debris.</p><p>Reserve&reg; Wood Extira&reg; doors arrive primed or painted, ready for installation, and Color Blast doors are backed by a two-year warranty for added confidence.</p><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-reserve-wood-extira.webp?sfvrsn=3d97e7ef_3\" alt=\"Reserve Wood Extira\" sf-size=\"100\" /><ol><li>Cladding</li><li>Extira&reg;</li><li>Polystyrene Insulated Hemlock Frame</li><li>1/4\" Luan Inside Skin</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Reserve Wood Extira","DisplayIndex":14,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/reserve-wood-extira","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>Your Reserve&reg; Wood Extira&reg; garage door comes primed and ready for the color of your choice. Thanks to Extira&rsquo;s ultra-smooth surface, each door takes paint beautifully, resulting in a rich, even finish that stands up to weather and wear.</p><p>Choose from hundreds of Sherwin-Williams&reg; paint shades with the Color Blast&reg; program including deep, dramatic hues that are tough to achieve on natural wood. Options range from classic white to a bold black&mdash;there&rsquo;s a color to complement your home and highlight your door&rsquo;s design details.\r\n</p><br />","TopSectionDisclaimer":"<p>Reserve&reg; Wood Extira&reg;\r\n    doors offer a range of window and top section options from classic rectangles\r\n    and squares to elegant arches and sleek modern designs. Go for a traditional\r\n    look with REC or SQ series windows or pick arched tops for a little extra\r\n    charm. For a contemporary look, try modern short, modern long, or the striking modern\r\n    aluminum inlay.\r\n</p><p>Each window style brings\r\n    in natural light while letting you choose the level of privacy and visual\r\n    impact you want. Pair your favorite design with specialty glass or opt for true\r\n    divided lite windows for authentic detail.\r\n</p>","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>Every Reserve® Wood Extira® garage door comes with sturdy spade lift handles, but you can personalize your door with a variety of handle and hinge designs. Choose from spade, spear, or colonial lift handles, each with its own distinct personality. Want more flair? Optional ring door knockers and escutcheon plates let you add even more character.</p>\r\n<p>Step plates and strap hinges are available in matching styles, giving your door a cohesive, handcrafted look. All hardware is made from premium materials designed to resist weather and everyday wear, so your door keeps looking great and operating smoothly.</p>\r\n","DesignDisclaimer":"<p>*Only available in smooth.</p>","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Reserve<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Wood Custom","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/reserve-le-chevron-595.webp?sfvrsn=2b65fc56_8","Id":"8","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/reserve-custom","DisplayIndex":15,"ShortDescription":"Both stunning and substantial, every Reserve® Wood garage door embodies our total commitment to design, detail and craftsmanship","AlternativeText":"Reserve Wood Custom"},{"Title":"Reserve<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Wood Limited Edition","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/reserve-limimted-edition-design5-arch1-meranti-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=d5180ef3_10","Id":"10","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/reserve","DisplayIndex":16,"ShortDescription":"Exceptional beauty, durability and energy efficiency","AlternativeText":"Reserve Wood Limited Edition"},{"Title":"Reserve<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Wood Modern","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/reserve-modern-design-cladding-solid-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=b04b7a7a_9","Id":"25","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/reserve-modern-contemporary-garage-doors","DisplayIndex":17,"ShortDescr